gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Far and far, Munijan roams, then Earth makes peace; 
Those holy people are pleased, extremely pure benefactors.

Here is the translation:

Arrived seems Lord's place, extremely joyful heart within;
Says, came our village, Hari fulfills friend's home.

Sat sangī ne sere sat, rahya rātya bhēlā bhagavant;
Ati ānadmāṁ gai reṇ, pachhi jāgiyā kamalaneṇ.

Those who are in the company of good people are indeed saints; having lived a night spent in devotion to God.

The two lines are:

Tart magavyo vaji te var, te par nath huya asvar;
Joee sim ne vadi saghli, pachhi naheene aaviyavali.

Translation:
He has won the battle, but lost his reputation; 
He has reached the border, but all his wealth is in vain.
